	* src/common.h (we_are_root): Remove extern decl; it's now static.
	* src/extract.c (we_are_root): Now static.
	* src/misc.c: Include <unlinkdir.h>.
	(remove_any_file): Use cannot_unlink_dir () rather than	we_are_root.

