	2003-11-14. Reason: Discussion with Paul Eggert and
	Jean-Louis Martineau. See also ChangeLog entry from
	1999-08-14.
	* tests/delete03.sh: Likewise.
	* tests/extrac04.sh: Likewise.
	* tests/multiv01.sh: Likewise.

