	to OLDGNU_FORMAT.
	* src/buffer.c: Use current_stat_info
	* src/compare.c: Likewise.
	* src/create.c: Likewise.
	* src/delete.c: Likewise.
	* src/incremen.c: Likewise.
	* src/mangle.c: Likewise.
